item.title: CVE-2023-36607|2024-08-02T16:52:53.640Z -- ovarro -- tbox%20rm2
item.description: The affected TBox RTUs are missing authorization for running some API commands. An attacker running these commands could reveal sensitive information such as software versions and web server file contents.
